{"Traces":[{"CenterLatitude":26.647662,"CenterLongitude":118.1843,"ZoomLevel":7,"Lines":[{"Markers":[{"Id":"15a8ca8a43f84302a40a17ebadc0becb","Latitude":26.647662,"Longitude":118.1843,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3507","Title":"南平"},{"Id":"ac4d14e7d53a4f1f85f78e2b0371d56d","Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封"},{"Id":"be172e0b460643379f9ae095bc636794","Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京"},{"Id":"16f18dfd8d2c449c93399743cd9475eb","Latitude":31.816791,"Longitude":119.980142,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3204","Title":"常州"},{"Id":"094990762f034affb9953174364abbf6","Latitude":26.647662,"Longitude":118.1843,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3507","Title":"南平"},{"Id":"a5658249bfa846e39439c9099975d31e","Latitude":27.756765,"Longitude":118.037551,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN350782001","Title":"崇安街道"},{"Id":"b410eaf6ae7f4c8c946ef02a7c3d0e4f","Latitude":26.647662,"Longitude":118.1843,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3507","Title":"南平"},{"Id":"6e66db50a62f434c995324a777b2b0f6","Latitude":27.337561,"Longitude":118.126953,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN350703","Title":"建阳"},{"Id":"0a0e1a71766d43cf9b486f95ed1ebbc4","Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州"},{"Id":"0761e608c2ff46f4a5d8a4ad5fd9bf50","Latitude":27.337561,"Longitude":118.126953,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN350703","Title":"建阳"}]}],"Markers":[{"Latitude":26.647662,"Longitude":118.1843,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3507","Title":"南平 (出生地)","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"15a8ca8a43f84302a40a17ebadc0becb\");'><span id='15a8ca8a43f84302a40a17ebadc0becb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1113')\">1091-1113年</a>，0-22岁</div><div id='15a8ca8a43f84302a40a17ebadc0becb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1091')\">1091年</a>，生于白水村。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1092&endYear=1095')\">1092-1095年</a>，居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1096&endYear=1096')\">1096年</a>，自幼强学，日诵数千言，耳目所接，一过不复忘。其为文肆笔而成，滂沛闳阔，凌厉顿挫，侪辈少能及之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1097&endYear=1107')\">1097-1107年</a>，居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1108&endYear=1108')\">1108年</a>，入州学。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1113')\">1109-1113年</a>，就读州学。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"094990762f034affb9953174364abbf6\");'><span id='094990762f034affb9953174364abbf6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1118&endYear=1126')\">1118-1126年</a>，27-35岁</div><div id='094990762f034affb9953174364abbf6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1118&endYear=1118')\">1118年</a>，太学之行，始阴习伊洛之学，继受易于谯定，归而请业于刘安世、杨时，融数家之学，以为己用，乃谢去场屋，归隐山田。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1119&endYear=1119')\">1119年</a>，居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1120&endYear=1121')\">1120-1121年</a>，居乡。有胡宪、刘子翚二君子之为道义交，并林之奇、魏掞之、范念德、朱熹诸子之问于学，复有山水田园、琴棋诗酒之陶其心，悠然度日。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1122&endYear=1122')\">1122年</a>，娶连氏。妇家富，无子，谋尽以赀归于女，勉之不受，以畀族之贤者，命之奉祀。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1123&endYear=1126')\">1123-1126年</a>，居乡。有胡宪、刘子翚二君子之为道义交，并林之奇、魏掞之、范念德、朱熹诸子之问于学，复有山水田园、琴棋诗酒之陶其心，悠然度日。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b410eaf6ae7f4c8c946ef02a7c3d0e4f\");'><span id='b410eaf6ae7f4c8c946ef02a7c3d0e4f_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1131&endYear=1132')\">1131-1132年</a>，40-41岁</div><div id='b410eaf6ae7f4c8c946ef02a7c3d0e4f' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1131&endYear=1132')\">1131-1132年</a>，居乡。有胡宪、刘子翚二君子之为道义交，并林之奇、魏掞之、范念德、朱熹诸子之问于学，复有山水田园、琴棋诗酒之陶其心，悠然度日。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ac4d14e7d53a4f1f85f78e2b0371d56d\");'><span id='ac4d14e7d53a4f1f85f78e2b0371d56d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1113&endYear=1118')\">1113-1118年</a>，22-27岁</div><div id='ac4d14e7d53a4f1f85f78e2b0371d56d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1113&endYear=1113')\">1113年</a>，以州学贡入太学。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1114&endYear=1114')\">1114年</a>，时蔡京用事，方禁士毋得挟元祐书，制师生收司连坐法，犯者罪至流徙。勉之心知其非是，阴访伊洛程氏之传，得其书，藏去。深夜，同舍生皆熟寐，乃始探箧解帙，下帷然膏，潜抄而默诵之。与胡宪交，相与问易于谯定。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1115&endYear=1118')\">1115-1118年</a>，置严诏于不顾，阴习伊洛之学，复与胡宪问易于谯定。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"be172e0b460643379f9ae095bc636794\");'><span id='be172e0b460643379f9ae095bc636794_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1118&endYear=1118')\">1118年</a>，27岁</div><div id='be172e0b460643379f9ae095bc636794' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1118&endYear=1118')\">1118年</a>，弃录牒，揖诸生而归，道南都，问学于刘安世。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.816791,"Longitude":119.980142,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3204","Title":"常州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"16f18dfd8d2c449c93399743cd9475eb\");'><span id='16f18dfd8d2c449c93399743cd9475eb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1118&endYear=1118')\">1118年</a>，27岁</div><div id='16f18dfd8d2c449c93399743cd9475eb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1118&endYear=1118')\">1118年</a>，过毗陵，请业于杨时。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":27.756765,"Longitude":118.037551,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN350782001","Title":"崇安街道","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a5658249bfa846e39439c9099975d31e\");'><span id='a5658249bfa846e39439c9099975d31e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1130')\">1127-1130年</a>，36-39岁</div><div id='a5658249bfa846e39439c9099975d31e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1130')\">1127-1130年</a>，居乡。有胡宪、刘子翚二君子之为道义交，并林之奇、魏掞之、范念德、朱熹诸子之问于学，复有山水田园、琴棋诗酒之陶其心，悠然度日。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":27.337561,"Longitude":118.126953,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN350703","Title":"建阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6e66db50a62f434c995324a777b2b0f6\");'><span id='6e66db50a62f434c995324a777b2b0f6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1138')\">1133-1138年</a>，42-47岁</div><div id='6e66db50a62f434c995324a777b2b0f6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1133')\">1133年</a>，乱后故山室庐荒颓，乃即建阳近郊萧屯别墅结草为堂，读书其中，力耕稼以自给，澹然若无求于世。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1134&endYear=1135')\">1134-1135年</a>，读书草堂，力耕稼以自给，澹然若无求于世。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1136')\">1136年4月</a>，有书寄胡寅，责其不尽孝于生身父母，由是胡寅之事，朝野尽知，历十余年，群议不息。<span class='label'>作品：</span>与胡寅书。<span class='inlineComment2'>（四川大学出版社2008（郭齐《朱子学新探》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1137&endYear=1138')\">1137-1138年</a>，读书草堂。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0761e608c2ff46f4a5d8a4ad5fd9bf50\");'><span id='0761e608c2ff46f4a5d8a4ad5fd9bf50_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1149')\">1138-1149年</a>，47-58岁</div><div id='0761e608c2ff46f4a5d8a4ad5fd9bf50' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，谢病归乡。以向之受召不阿权贵，士人美之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1139&endYear=1139')\">1139年</a>，赵鼎出知泉州，谒而叹重之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1140&endYear=1140')\">1140年</a>，与朱松交。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1141')\">1141年</a>，有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>翁彦深行状。<span class='inlineComment2'>（四川大学出版社2008（郭齐《朱子学新探》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1142&endYear=1142')\">1142年</a>，居草堂。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1143&endYear=1143')\">1143年</a>，春，友人朱松死，遗命其子朱熹禀学于刘勉之等人之门。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1144&endYear=1144')\">1144年</a>，有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>祭刘子翼文。<span class='inlineComment2'>（四川大学出版社2008（郭齐《朱子学新探》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1145&endYear=1145')\">1145年</a>，居草堂。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1146&endYear=1146')\">1146年</a>，有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>祭刘子羽文。<span class='inlineComment2'>（四川大学出版社2008（郭齐《朱子学新探》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1146&endYear=1146')\">1146年</a>，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>挽刘子羽诗二首。<span class='inlineComment2'>（四川大学出版社2008（郭齐《朱子学新探》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1147&endYear=1147')\">1147年</a>，春，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>与林之奇书数首。<span class='inlineComment2'>（四川大学出版社2008（郭齐《朱子学新探》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1147&endYear=1147')\">1147年</a>，冬，友人刘子翚死，病中为诗并序以挽之。<span class='label'>作品：</span>挽刘子翚诗。<span class='inlineComment2'>（四川大学出版社2008（郭齐《朱子学新探》））</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1147&endYear=1147')\">1147年</a>，以女妻朱熹。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1148&endYear=1148')\">1148年</a>，居草堂。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1149&endYear=1149')\">1149年2月20日</a>，终于建阳之里第。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0a0e1a71766d43cf9b486f95ed1ebbc4\");'><span id='0a0e1a71766d43cf9b486f95ed1ebbc4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，47岁</div><div id='0a0e1a71766d43cf9b486f95ed1ebbc4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年</a>，四月，户部侍郎李弥逊、权刑部侍郎曾开、给事中吴表臣、张致远、中书舍人句涛、吕本中奏勉之可用，诏召赴行在。十月至临安，不得面上，乃谢病归。<br /></div>"}],"Title":"刘勉之 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1091-1149)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：郭齐《朱熹岳父刘勉之事迹考》　录入整理：彭洁明</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 5, 117.147023, 30.7253015, 7)\">0-35岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">南平</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">南京</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">常州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">南平</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(5, 10, 119.099622, 28.4638605, 9)\">36-58岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">崇安街道</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">南平</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">建阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">建阳</a></p>"}]}